me.Abhigya.core.util.configurable.location

Class ConfigurableLocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bukkit.Location
      • me.Abhigya.core.util.configurable.location.ConfigurableLocation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, Configurable, Initializable, Loadable, Saveable, Validable, org.bukkit.configuration.serialization.ConfigurationSerializable

    public class ConfigurableLocation
extends org.bukkit.Location
implements Configurable, Initializable
    Represents a Location that is 'Configurable' because can be loaded from/saved on a ConfigurationSection.

      • of

        public static ConfigurableLocation of(org.bukkit.configuration.ConfigurationSection section)
        Returns a ConfigurableLocation loaded from the given ConfigurationSection, or null if there is no any valid ConfigurableLocation stored on the given ConfigurationSection.

        Note that this method checks the given configuration section calling isConfigurableLocation(ConfigurationSection).

        Parameters:
        section - Section to parse
        Returns:
        Parsed location
